  "description": "<i>Bloody Sands</i> is a 1kb game participant in the 2011 Minigame Competition. As a truck driver the player is taking part in a dangerous military mission. The task requires traversing the subsequent stages of the desert full of buried Improvised Explosive Devices. The game is all about maneuvering between dangerous objects. The truck may be moved up, down, forward and backward. The bar at the top of the screen shows the remaining distance to the end of the stage.",
